  "instructions": [
    "Whisk flour, water, and tandoori spice blend to form a thick batter. Brush vegetable oil onto lettuce leaves.",
    "Dip each leaf into the tandoori dough mixture until coated evenly. Allow to sit for 30 seconds.",
    "Fry in a shallow pan over medium heat until golden brown on both sides, about 1 minute per side.",
    "Combine low-sodium soy sauce and lemon juice in a small bowl, season with black pepper, then drizzle over warm wraps."
